    "summary": "KEEP \"impels\" — different Chinese source, my flag was wrong",
    "content": "**KEEP \"impels.\"**\n\nI was wrong to flag it. The Chinese is genuinely different: 推动 (push/drive) in the footnote is stronger than 想要 (want to) in the body. The translator correctly matched register to source — \"impels\" for 推动, \"moves me to want to\" for 使得我想要. Harmonizing would erase a real distinction in the original.\n\nGood catch on the different source texts."
  }
}
